name: Simple WWT Units Interactive Model
short_description:
SWTUIM is a Simple Wastewater Treatment Units Interactive Model for hydraulic and structural design of WWT plants.
Project started as a research project submitted in complete fulfilment of the requirements for the degree of Doctor of Philosophy in Environmental Engineering, Sudan University of Science and Technology.
By: Eng. Hisham Isam Mohamed Abdel-Magid,
Supervised by: Dr. Eng. Yousif Ali Yousif,
Co-supervised by: Dr. Eng. Alsadig Alhadi Alhasan
summary: Simple Wastewater Treatment Units Interactive Model
